items.title: Tickets going on sale for Bill Maher show at Comerica Theatre
items.summary:
For more than 20 years, Bill Maher has set the boundaries of where funny, political talk can go on American television.   He is bringing this talk on tour with him and will make a stop in Phoenix at Comerica Theatre on Saturday, February 24th at 8pm.  Tickets go on sale next Friday, September 22nd at 10am at ticketmaster.com, the box office and all Ticketmaster outlets.  To charge by phone call 800-745-3000.  All tickets are!

The post Tickets going on sale for Bill Maher show at Comerica Theatre appeared first on AZ Big Media.
